name: MaterialNameless
tagline: MaterialNameless is a Material Design theme for NamelessMC, a project by @samerton.
body:
# Welcome to MaterialNameless
Introducing, [@samerton's NamelessMC](https://github.com/samerton/NamelessMC/) with Material Design!

## What is Material Design?
Material Design is a design concept and specification created by Google for the Android OS. You can see the design guide here: [https://material.google.com](https://material.google.com/#).
According to their site, the goals are to provide a design that is native to all screen sizes and to bridge the gap between virtual design and reality (to make movement and animation more realistic.)
